OL,7,FJoshua and his mum, Sarah, have been
OL,8,Fspeaking to ITV Granada Reports
OL,9,Fjournalist Lucille Brobbey.
OL,11,FA teenager who suffers multiple
OL,12,Fseizures a day says he is "really
OL,13,Fscared" for his safety after funding
OL,14,Ffor a personal support worker who
OL,15,Faccompanies him on his journey to
OL,16,Fcollege was withdrawn.
OL,18,FJoshua Richmond has relied on a
OL,19,Fcouncil funded personal assistant (PA)
OL,20,Ffor the past six years to support him
OL,21,Fon his taxi journey to and from school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
