OL,3,CTeen who suffers daily seizures
OL,4,C'scared' for safety after transport
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe 16-year-old, from Rochdale,
OL,8,FGreater Manchester, has epilepsy and
OL,9,Fcannot travel on his own.
OL,11,FJoshua is set to begin his new BTEC
OL,12,FSports course at college on 1
OL,13,FSeptember but his mum, Sarah Richmond-
OL,14,FBunnel, says with without a chaperone,
OL,15,Fthere would be no one to look after
OL,16,Fhim if he had a seizure.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
