OL,4,C'scared' for safety after transport
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FRochdale Borough Council has said that
OL,8,Fthe driver will be instructed to pull
OL,9,Fover safely and provide support as
OL,10,Fappropriate while emergency services
OL,11,Fare contacted.
OL,13,FHowever, Sarah says this is "not
OL,14,Ffeasible" and is now desperate to get
OL,15,Fthe local authority to reverse the
OL,16,Fdecision so that Joshua is able to get
OL,17,Fto college safely.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
