OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FA spokesperson from Rochdale Borough
OL,8,FCouncil said: "While it is
OL,9,Finappropriate to comment on individual
OL,10,Fcases, Rochdale Borough Council takes
OL,11,Fgreat care in managing all assisted
OL,12,Ftravel requests for children and young
OL,13,Fpeople with special educational needs
OL,14,Fand or disabilities.
OL,16,F"Every application we receive is
OL,17,Fthoughtfully considered to understand
OL,18,Fthe level of support a young person
OL,19,Fmay need in order to attend school or
OL,20,Fcollege.
