OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"While families have the right to
OL,8,Fappeal this decision, the council also
OL,9,Fprovides a post-16 SEND travel
OL,10,Fassistance offer to support local
OL,11,Ffamilies further, including
OL,12,Findependent travel training, fuel
OL,13,Fallowance and a personal travel
OL,14,Fbudget, as we work to ensure children
OL,15,Fand young people feel safe and
OL,16,Fsupported when they are travelling."
OL,18,FSarah has now appealed the decision
OL,19,Fand has been informed by the council
OL,20,Fthat it will take a further 15 days
OL,21,Ffor them to respond.
